{{Infobox dungeon |name = Mt. Ember Summit |image = [[File:Mt. Ember Summit.png|thumb]] |caption = A map of Mt. Ember Summit. |tokens = 1,750 |location = Sevii Island 1. }} '''Mt. Ember Summit''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Kanto]]. It has 25 tiles arranged in a 5x5 square, including 5 chest tiles, 13 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile. Wild Encounters have 18,120 HP.
